additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Keep out of reach of children. Irritant. DO NOT SWALLOW. Causes serious eye damage and skin irritation. Avoid contact with eyes and skin. FIST AID; For advise contact the Poisons Information Centre (Phone Australia 131126; New Zealand:0800764766) or a doctor. If swallowed, seek medical advice immediately and show this container or label. In case of contact with eyes or skin, rinse immediately with plenty of water, If irritation persists, contact a doctor. Do not mix with other products. Suitable for all dishwashers. Do not add detergent.
